'''印度國防部'''（[[IAST|IAST]]：''Rakshā Maṃtrālaya''，英語：'''Ministry of Defence'''，'''MoD'''），是[[印度政府|印度政府]]行政部門之一，主要負責統合國防與陸海空軍。[[印度總統|印度總統]]擔任[[印度武裝部隊|武裝部隊]]的最高統帥。印度國防部下屬部門包括包括[[印度陸軍|印度陸軍]]，[[印度海軍|印度海軍]]，[[印度空軍|印度空軍]]和[[印度海岸警衛隊|印度海岸警衛隊]]。印度國防部預算目前在世界排名第三<ref name="IDSA budget">{{cite web|url=https://idsa.in/issuebrief/defence-budget-2018-19-controlling-manpower-cost-lkbehera-020218|title=Defence Budget 2018-19: The Imperative of Controlling Manpower Cost|last=Behera|first=Laxman K.|date=2 February 2018|website=[[Institute_for_Defence_Studies_and_Analyses|Institute for Defence Studies and Analyses]]|language=en|access-date=19 February 2018|archive-date=2020-12-30|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201230175221/https://idsa.in/issuebrief/defence-budget-2018-19-controlling-manpower-cost-lkbehera-020218|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="The Hindu budget">{{Cite news|url=http://www.thehindu.com/business/budget/modest-hike-in-defence-budget-pensions-see-sharp-rise/article22622364.ece|title=Modest hike in defence budget, pensions see sharp rise|last=Peri|first=Dinakar|date=1 February 2018|work=[[The_Hindu|The Hindu]]|access-date=19 February 2018|publication-place=New Delhi|language=en|issn=0971-751X|oclc=13119119|archive-date=2020-11-09|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201109041124/https://www.thehindu.com/business/budget/modest-hike-in-defence-budget-pensions-see-sharp-rise/article22622364.ece|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="The Times of India budget">{{Cite news|url=https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/india/budget-2018-govt-hikes-defence-budget-by-7-81/articleshow/62740525.cms|title=Budget 2018: Govt hikes defence budget by 7.81%, but it's just 1.58% of GDP & lowest since 1962|last=Pandit|first=Rajat|date=1 February 2018|work=[[The_Times_of_India|The Times of India]]|access-date=18 February 2018|publication-place=New Delhi|oclc=23379369|archive-date=2020-12-18|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201218180005/https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/india/budget-20